{"tid":1114513,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"終於幫女神買到演唱會飛","createTime":"2019-04-18T13:21:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-18T15:25:28.000Z","uid":65603,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0a49ecec8b55c4ee844aff94a20ea0e66b0993e3","tid":1114513,"uid":65603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T13:21:59.000Z","msg":"之前同女神傾計既時候得知佢鍾意嗰個歌星準備開演唱會，咁我就自告奮勇同佢講話幫佢買，女神即刻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之後我再打蛇隨棍上咁問佢買2張好唔好，佢又再<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n於是我前日凌晨就走到排隊，務求買到靚位。我一路排既時候就一路ff到時同女神一齊睇演唱會既快樂時光<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />皇天不負有心人，排咗9個鐘終於買到2張山頂位，$780既飛！<br />\n我今朝就約咗女神去俾張飛佢，點知佢話：「誠仔，多謝你呀，哩度$1560！」 之後佢就拎走咗嗰2張飛，原來佢係諗住同學霸一齊去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想問下大家我應該點同女神講話其實佢仲差我total係$1576，因為每張飛要$8手續費<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dfd1ba2969f0b7e419c1afd76f31ca8b411515d","tid":1114513,"uid":192491,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T13:24:57.000Z","msg":"請問關許志安咩事?"},{"pid":"0e840a6c5254f039f56ed1ae7af0a33b1af9c03f","tid":1114513,"uid":65603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9dfd1ba2969f0b7e419c1afd76f31ca8b411515d","tid":1114513,"uid":192491,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T13:24:57.000Z","msg":"請問關許志安咩事?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T13:27:07.000Z","msg":"我同佢一樣都係冇咗靈魂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f54f1cdd4bc939aa9ab6b80e29a163ec2b218f1","tid":1114513,"uid":247836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T13:28:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a4b5388ac0879751bbefaf2d08496ca6ce47725a","tid":1114513,"uid":65603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f54f1cdd4bc939aa9ab6b80e29a163ec2b218f1","tid":1114513,"uid":247836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T13:28:21.000Z","msg"